snippet.title: Kungfu Cowboy Trailer
snippet.description:
Now out on Steam Early Access March 25th! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1499220/Kungfu_Cowboy/

Kungfu Cowboy is a quirky, challenging run 'n' gun coop platformer with roguelike elements. Explore randomly generated levels, unlock hidden "gunfu" powers and customize your weapon with unique builds. Will y'all make it to the saloon in one piece?

Official Website: https://soyboygames.com
Follow Soy Boy Games on https://twitter.com/soyboygames
Join Our Discord Community: https://discord.com/invite/dYBWARz
